    <h1><%= recipe.title %></h1>
    <h2>Here you will find the recipe for <%= recipe.title %>:</h2>

    <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>1 cup bulgur wheat</li>
        <li>2 cups water</li>
        <li>1/2 cup parsley, chopped</li>
        <li>1 tomato, diced</li>
        <li>1 onion, diced</li>
        <li>Juice of 1 lemon</li>
        <li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Instructions:</h2>
    <p>
        1. Boil water and pour over bulgur in a bowl. Let it sit for 20 minutes.
        <br>
        2. Fluff with a fork and add parsley, tomato, onion, lemon juice, salt, and pepper.
        <br>
        3. Mix well and serve chilled.
    </p>
  

